Mank | Image: Netflix Here are the nominees in key categories for the 78th Golden Globe Awards, which will be handed out in Beverly Hills on February 28. Netflix’s “Mank”, set in Hollywood’s Golden Age about the making of “Citizen Kane”, led all films with six nominations. The streaming service crushed the competition with 22 overall nods. Comedians Tina Fey and Amy Poehler will be back to host the event, the first major awards show of a pandemic-era season that culminates with the Oscars on April 25. See the list of the nominees below: FILM Best Motion Picture — Musical or Comedy
